platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Keep meaning to read more, but just can’t find the time? This is where you’ll find thousands of summaries with key insights you can read or listen to in digestible 15-minute Blinks.
如果你一直想閱讀更多文字，但卻找不到時間，這個 App 就可以幫到你。只需 15 分鐘，即可閱讀或聆聽數以千計個簡單易懂、涵蓋重要見解的摘要。
